Html:
When I try and try and swap out gems the options are empy. I right-click on a piece of gear and selet edit custom gemming, the only gem in the filter is the one that I already have on.
All the gems in the gemming template are selected and the 'disable gems' in the filter is not selected. Im sure its something silly Im overlooking but I can think of it.

And theres one other thing, Im building an Enhanced set of gear on Rawr, is there any way to make it not show spell power gear in the comparison window?

You have gems filtered out; check your filters (top right).

Make sure you're in the Enhance model when making your Enhance set. If you're still seeing spellpower gear, it's because it's actually good gear.
The gems that I have filtered out are world drop, pvp, BoP and green level perfect gems. I unchecked them all and I still get nothing.
Keep looking through your filters. What you describe is exactly what happens when you have them filtered out.
The main Other filter has to be checked
